<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="equally-adv">equally <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'iːkwəli/    美 /'iːkwəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>相等地；同样地；平等地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People are born equal and should be treated equally.
人生来平等，应该同等对待。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Men and women must be treated <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (平等地) in education and employment.   （2014 陕西）  </li>
<li>Anyone, whether he is an official or a bus driver, should be <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (equal) respected.  （2012 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. equally  2. equally  </p></div>